124
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,290
Would he still be locked up?

125
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,340
What does that tell you?

126
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:57,580
They control everything!

127
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,170
The more you push back,
the harder they press.

128
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,540
Me pushing back?

129
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,340
I'm not the problem here!

130
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,660
What did we do wrong?

131
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,580
Pushing back?

132
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:07,290
You're just scared, that's all.

133
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,900
What's the use of being scared?

134
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,810
Scared or not,

135
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,850
those people want you dead!

136
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:13,700
If you don't comply,

137
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,850
they'll destroy you!

138
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,660
Then so be it!

139
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,930
Like my dad said,

140
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,580
better to die on your feet
than live on your knees!

141
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,370
So tell me who they are,

142
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,370
I'll confront them myself!

143
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,780
Let me deal with them!

144
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,540
You're not going anywhere!

145
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,370
Let go of me, you coward!

146
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,460
I'll hit...

147
00:08:27,870 --> 00:08:28,460
Hit me!

148
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,020
Go ahead!

149
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,980
Hit me if you want,

150
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,180
