151
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,100
Come on, hit me!

152
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,770
Just listen to me, okay?

153
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,530
I'm begging you, please!

154
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,940
Don't go out there!

155
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:01,730
