156
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:02,180
Uncle...

157
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,060
I...

158
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,820
Chao, stay inside!

159
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,340
Let go of me!

160
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,180
Let me go!

161
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,010
Let go!

162
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:07,980
Let me go!

163
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,980
- Chao!
- Let me...

164
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:10,580
Mr. Wan,

165
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:11,770
