this whole time, huh?

167
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,420
Well...

168
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,340
Uncle!

169
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,940
Is that him?

170
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,420
Get him.

171
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:18,010
Chao!

172
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,250
Chao, run!

173
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,490
Chao, get out!

174
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:43,700
Get him!

175
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:50,730
Chao, run!

176
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:08,460
Stop!

177
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,460
Stay there!

178
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,580
Go ahead, hit me!

179
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,580
Chao!

180
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,610
Are you okay?

181
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,060
You sure can run, huh?

182
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,610
Stop! That's enough!

183
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,130
Come at me!

184
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,300
Take them!

185
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:53,650
Sir,

186
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:54,700
wait...

187
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:55,340
Move it!

188
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,370
Who sent you?

189
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,130
Cut the crap!

190
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:57,730
Get in!

191
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:59,250
Mr. Chen is my friend.

192
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,060
You...

193
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,610
In the car!

194
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,180
Get in!

195
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:01,820
