from around that area.

209
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,650
Jinhai KTV?

210
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:31,980
What case is that for?

211
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,610
Still my brother's case.

212
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:36,730
It's confirmed now.

213
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:38,850
Jinhai KTV

214
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:41,370
is where my brother

215
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:42,850
actually died.

216
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:46,340
We checked all around it.

217
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,060
No useful leads so far.

218
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,580
So, what now?

219
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,460
I'll keep digging.

220
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:03,370
Qin Feng,

221
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,370
you said your piece
outside my place the other day

222
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,010
and then just walked away.

223
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,820
Don't you want to hear my side?

224
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,300
You called yourself a coward,

225
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:34,530
but you know what I see?

226
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:37,530
Honestly,

227
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:39,370
I think deep down, you're a fighter.

228
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,460
You just never give yourself any credit.

229
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,580
That day, you said

230
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,850
you didn't deserve to like me.

231
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,700
But that's not
for anyone else to decide,

232
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,530
it's up to you.

233
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,130
If you can't believe in yourself,

234
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,610
