235
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,650
That's my answer.

236
00:14:14,630 --> 00:14:16,180
So, nothing you want to say to me?

237
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,100
I'm giving you one more chance.

238
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,340
Thank you, Jing,

239
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,940
for telling me all this.

240
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:37,980
Hopeless idiot.

241
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,010
Yanxin,

242
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,530
