245
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,370
Alright, I'm just outside your place.

246
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,060
What's with you lately?

247
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,180
You only show up when Zijian's gone?

248
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,300
You sure you're my brother?

249
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,060
What's up? Have a seat.

250
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,370
Nothing, really.

251
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:17,980
So,

252
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,100
how are things with you two lately?

253
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,650
We're fine.

254
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:25,580
He's been great,

255
00:15:25,870 --> 00:15:26,850
just super busy.

256
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,850
He didn't even have time to help me

257
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:30,650
choose a wedding planner.

258
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,530
Wedding planner?

259
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,460
That's just the start.

260
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,130
I had to pick the venue,

261
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,130
the honeymoon location,

262
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,370
book every flight and hotel—

263
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,940
did it all by myself.

264
00:15:43,030 --> 00:15:43,820
So,

265
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,340
what's keeping him so busy anyway?

266
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,850
Tianlong's business, what else?

267
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:49,980
I'm telling you,

268
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:51,530
Zijian is practically

269
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:53,220
running that place.

270
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:55,010
