271
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:56,180
If you ask me,

272
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:57,370
Tianlong would be lost

273
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,940
without him.

274
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,010
He's their future.

275
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,010
How's that?

276
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,580
You know, Long's trying

277
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,100
to get into the clean energy business?

278
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:08,370
Zijian and Yun's connections

279
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:09,420
saved him so much trouble.

280
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:12,460
Yun even introduced him

281
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:15,180
to Wanchuan Mining,

282
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,530
got Long's project moving.

283
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,820
Without Zijian,

284
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,820
he'd have to start from scratch—

285
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,730
even $500 million wouldn't be enough.

286
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:24,420
So that house of yours

287
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:26,300
is really nothing to worry about.

288
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:29,100
Long just wanted to show some goodwill.

289
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:30,490
Sometimes I wonder

290
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:32,100
if those childhood fevers
fried your brain.

291
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,340
Come on,

